data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the exclusive Ladera Community! This magnificent 4 bedroom, 3 bath oasis will take your breath away from the moment you step inside. Situated on a serene greenbelt, this home offers a peaceful and private retreat while still being a part of a gated community with amenities galore. Step inside the front door and be greeted by an open and airy floor plan that is perfect for entertaining or simply enjoying quality time with your loved ones. With 2884 square feet of living space, there is plenty of room for everyone to spread out and relax. The bedrooms in this home are unlike anything you'll find in the new builds going up in the subdivision. They are generously sized and provide a peaceful sanctuary for rest and relaxation. Imagine spending your evenings sipping a cold drink on the covered back porch, which comes equipped with a gas line that is just waiting for your outdoor kitchen dreams to become a reality. And speaking of convenience, the electrical package in this home ensures that you will always have an outlet nearby for all your lighting and exterior decorating needs. But the perks of this home don't stop there. The upstairs bedroom closet and garage are both equipped with an installed container system, providing you with the ultimate in organization and storage solutions. Located in the coveted Medina Valley ISD, this home is also just a short walk away from a neighborhood school, making it perfect for families who value education and convenience. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this dream home your own. Schedule a showing today and prepare to fall in love with everything this home has to offer.
